Value Required USERNAME (\S+)
Value Required PASSWORD (\S+)
Value Required VPNCUSTOMER (\S+)
Value Required VPNLOGINS (\S+)

Start
  ^username ${USERNAME} password ${PASSWORD} .+
  ^username ${USERNAME} attributes
  ^\s+vpn-group-policy ${VPNCUSTOMER}
  ^\s+vpn-simultaneous-logins ${VPNLOGINS} -> Record
